parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the list to update.

parameters.name: elements
parameters.description: One or more list elements to add or replace. If you are providing the elements, make sure to specify the updateMode to use. If you are deleting all elements from the list, use REPLACE for the updateMode and provide an empty list (0 elements). (string) ---

parameters.name: updateMode
parameters.description: The update mode (type). Use APPEND if you are adding elements to the list. Use REPLACE if you replacing existing elements in the list. Use REMOVE if you are removing elements from the list.

parameters.name: variableType
parameters.description: The variable type you want to assign to the list.
